main.name: Wayne Ji
main.description: Programmer and analyst with a data driven mindset
main.bio: Chances are if you are reading this, I have applied for a job or you have seen my resume. I just graduated from university in May 2021, and am looking for an opportunity to apply my skills. What I lack in experience I make up with the ability to learn at an accelerated rate. I have a laser focus and dedication to complete any task to the best of my ability. In my free time I like to catch up on competitive Valorant or even play the occasional game myself. Reach out to me if you have any questions, or just talk gaming.
